author: wn.com
title: Pennsylvania Senate to launch removal proceedings against Attorney General Kathleen Kane
text: A special state Senate committee will be empaneled next week to start the process of determining whether embattled Attorney General Kathleen Kane should be removed from office. Senate President Pro Tempore Joseph Scarnati , R-Jefferson
